<h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #111827; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600;">Hey <%= @user.name %>,</h2>

<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
  Someone requested a reset of your password. If this was you, click the button below to set a new password:
</p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
  <tr>
    <td align="center">
      <a href="<%= @url %>" style="background-color: #2563eb; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px;">
        Reset Password
      </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 0;">
  This link will expire in 2 hours.
</p>
<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 8px;">
  If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:<br>
  <span style="word-break: break-all; color: #2563eb;"><%= @url %></span>
</p>
